- `docs/source/screen-spec.md` S21
- `docs/source/api-contracts.md` §§6.2, 8.1, 25.3, and §44
- `docs/source/codebase-design.md` §§7.2, 23.3-23.5, 26.1-26.3, 27.1, and 36.1
